	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />At scales like this (1px = 25mm), mitten hands are unavoidable because you can't fit four distinct fingers into four pixels. But at least make a suggestion of a thumb.<br /><br />I'll need some time to look over these pics and see what details to change, as well as expected width of a head side-to-side vs. front-to-back. I might have to strip her down and refine the underlying &quot;doll base&quot;, as some pixel artists call it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
